```plantuml
@startuml IBM_customer-sentiment-on-seller-quality-nlu-cp4d

actor User
participant "Jupyter Notebook" as Notebook
participant "Watson NLU" as NLU
participant "Db2 Database" as Db2
participant "Embedded Dashboard" as Dashboard

User -> Notebook: Execute analysis pipeline
Notebook -> Db2: Fetch customer reviews
Db2 --> Notebook: Return review data
Notebook -> NLU: Analyze sentiment/emotion (reviews)
NLU --> Notebook: Return sentiment scores
Notebook -> Notebook: Calculate seller ratings
Notebook -> Dashboard: Push visualization data
Dashboard --> User: Display interactive insights

@enduml
```